headline: Is There Opportunity for BRO After Share Price Dip and Earnings Beat in 2025?
summary: Trying to figure out what to do with Brown & Brown stock? You are not alone. Whether you are already a shareholder or just watching from the sidelines, there is a lot to unpack. While the stock has slipped a bit lately, dropping 2.7% this week, 4.6% over the past month, and 9.6% year-to-date, it is easy to forget the bigger picture. In fact, Brown & Brown is still up an impressive 50.9% over the last three years and a remarkable 111.3% over five years. Are these recent dips a red flag, or...
